widgets_values: If you want to change aanything except what is masked, you can use the mask inverted here. Connect it to the "mask" of Grow Mask with Blur

nodes.title: Read before starting!
widgets_values:
Update the Model Loaders before continuing!!

Either Bypass the Resize Image Node or set the Height and width

Remeber you must use a *Wan Approved* resolution. That info can be found on the huggingface page for each model

Enable Model Loaders = Always On
Enable Load Video = Always On
1. Enable Get First Frames - Run and Save Image
2. Enable Inpaint First Frame - Run and Save Image
3. Enable Inpaint Video + Automasking - Video is Inpainted!
Use this for automasking, use mask from load image if masking manually. Just update where it says "person" with the thing you want to mask.
<- To learn how to use this click the tool tip!
